head.note:
In English, Spanish, Portuguese, and French;
                        English text, only, printed. Ratification advised by the Senate, May 24
                        (legislative day of May 10), 1934; ratified by the President, June 30, 1934;
                        ratification of the United States deposited with the Pan American Union,
                        July 13, 1934; proclaimed by the President, October 11, 1934.
